none: media/user/SCRAPE/test/2021-05-walrus/extracted/Walrus/09 Putting The Pow! Back In Powerviolence

Originally ripped by Terminal Escape, posted on May 29, 2021 Description from Terminal Escape:
Not suitable for the faint at heart or the discerning listener, this excretion from WALRUS is a straight edge shit-fi boombox attack from a long gone era of not giving a shit. Grinds and blasts and manic fastcore and would-be gnarly breakdowns all fight a losing battle with fidelity on Tuskill...but maybe victory isn't really the goal here. Perhaps the fight itself is the whole fucking point.  TUSKILL
